

Podcast via http://www.archive.org/details/Autonomo.usPodcastEpisode2InterviewWithJimmyWalesOfWikia


=Description=

"Second episode of the podcast for autonomo.us, a loose group investigating Free Network Services. In this episode we discuss Richard Stallman's quotes in a recent article in the Guardian (http://ur1.ca/7as) and our efforts to make our own Web site (http://ur1.ca/duy) a Free Service. We also interview Jimmy Wales (http://ur1.ca/duz) about Wikia Search (http://ur1.ca/10), his company's project to create a Free Network Service for Web search.


This audio is part of the collection: [http://www.archive.org/details/opensource_audio Open Source Audio]"
(http://www.archive.org/details/Autonomo.usPodcastEpisode2InterviewWithJimmyWalesOfWikia)


